                                <h1>Coronavirus COVID-19 Information</h1>
                                
                                
                                <p>This page is designed to provide CHSD117 parents, students, and staff, the latest information regarding the Coronavirus COVID-19 in our area. Please be aware that we will update this page regularly with the most current information as we receive it from the Centers for Disease Control (CDC), Illinois Department of Public Health (IDPH), Lake County Health Department. </p>

<p>See <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/index.html">CDC</a>Â  and <a href="http://www.dph.illinois.gov/">IDPH</a>. <strong>Frequent review of the CDC and IDPH guidance and recommendations related to COVID-19 (Coronavirus) is advisable for all as this is a fluid situation. </strong></p>

